


bezout(8)                      Scilab Function                      bezout(8)






NAME
  bezout - Bezout equation for polynomials

CALLING SEQUENCE
  [gcd,U]=bezout(p1,p2)

PARAMETERS

  p1, p2    : two real polynomials

DESCRIPTION
  [gcd,U]=bezout(p1,p2) computes GCD gcd of p1 and p2 and in addition a (2x2)
  unimodular matrix U such that:

  [p1,p2]*U = [gcd,0]

  The lcm of p1 and p2 is given by:

  p1*U(1,2) (or -p2*U(2,2))

SEE ALSO
  poly, roots, simpl, cleanp, lcm


































